record.primary_description:
With more than 60,000 taxis covering all 47 prefectures (*1) of Japan, JapanTaxi is the ultimate taxi app you ever need in Japan! Tap to call a taxi, make a reservation or find your fare instantly. Paying your fare is easy! Connect your preferred payment method (credit cards, Apple Pay or other payment options) to the Online Payment feature to order, ride and pay blissfully hassle-free!
*1 As of October, 2018.

About JapanTaxi App
1. Call a Taxi
Select your pickup location on the app to request a taxi. You can customize your order by selecting a drop-off location, a number of vehicles, type of vehicle and payment method. When your order matches with a nearby taxi, it will give you an estimated time of arrival. It’s that easy!

2. Make a Reservation
Place an order in advance and give yourself a piece of mind. After selecting the date and time, just follow the same steps as “Call a Taxi.”

3. Fare Finder
Go to Calculate Fare and enter pick-up and drop-off locations. We will show you an estimated fare and travel time. *The actual fare will vary depending on traffic, road conditions and route taken.

4. Airport Fixed Rate
Travel smart with our Airport Fixed Rate! The flat rate taxi service is available in selected cities and the fee may vary by participating taxi company.

5. JapanTaxi Wallet and Cashless Payment Options
Link your payment method to your JapanTaxi account and pay your fare seamlessly. The Online Payment feature accepts credit cards and other online payment services. (*2)
*2 As of August 2019, the following services are available; Apple Pay, credit cards,d payment and Google Pay.
*3 As of August 2018, JapanTaxi Wallet is available in 4,500 NihonKotsu taxis equipped with the electronic tablet within the 23 districts of Tokyo and Musashino city and Mitaka city.

Note
・This application requires network service and GPS.
・The current version requires iOS 11 or newer.
・Orders placed through this app is the same as requesting a taxi by a phone call. As such, some taxi companies may add a Radio Dispatch Fee to your fare total.
・Ride availability depends on an area, weather and road condition.
・Fare Calculation is based on the calculated route offered by Google Map Service. Therefore, the actual route may vary. Estimated fare does not include tolls, radio dispatch fees, and/or reservation fees.
・Please check the participating taxi companies and service areas before making an order.
・Some of the in-app functions are only available with participating taxi companies. Some taxi companies do not receive drop-off location data or offer advanced reservations or cashless payment options.
・Campaigns are not affiliated in any way with Apple.
record.name: JapanTaxi

TrustVault: The insured crypto custody wallet for individual investors looking for a safer, faster and easier way to send, receive, buy and keep safe their cryptocurrencies.

Billions of dollars worth of cryptocurrency have been lost or stolen. Investors need a wallet, therefore, with bank-grade security that doesn’t compromise on speed, ease-of-use or access.  Introducing TrustVault by Trustology.  

We go about safeguarding crypto assets in a completely different, highly effective and unique way compared to other companies in our sector. Built with institutions in mind, our secure product essentially goes beyond ‘cold storage’ at ‘hot wallet’ speed - less than one second to process transactions. We do this by leveraging an infrastructure of hardware security modules (HSMs) with additional built in firmware, secure data centres and multiple levels of encryption to mitigate security risks to enable our users with the most secure, lightning fast way to execute transactions through their mobile device, web or via API integrations. Unlike a hardware or software wallet, TrustVault accounts can always be recovered, even when the mobile device is lost or stolen. This is because your assets' private keys are always kept hardware-secure in our tamper proof data centre hosted HSM cluster and never in the device.

You can use the TrustVault app to send, receive and buy Bitcoin (BTC), Ethereum (ETH) and selected ERC20 tokens (ZRX, HOT, BAT, SAI, DAI, VXV, MKR, USDT, OMG, REP, LINK) as well as Binance (BNB) and other third party tokens supported on their chain.  We are the first custodial wallet to integrate with MetaMask giving you secure access to Ethereum dApps so you can access your assets knowing you are kept super safe. 

It takes less than five minutes to set up your TrustVault account and it's done through the user-friendly app itself. If you need any help along the way, we offer live chat support during UK business hours (9am till 5pm), including account recovery.

TrustVault is developed by Trustology, an insured crypto custodial wallet provider based in London, UK.

Earn money with the ATM.com® app by matching with brands. Our unique Brand Matching feature gives you the ability to earn extra cash using your phone!
Build your profile with the ATM app by answering questions about yourself. We never share or sell your answers - we use it to match you with top brands and unlock opportunities for you to earn. Brands pay ATM.com for your interest and we share that money with you. You can earn more rewards and cash back by engaging with your favorite brands.
ATM.com® is a free service with no monthly or annual fee and helps you save and make money online. ATM.com does not sell your personal information (our limited rights to share your personal information are described in our Privacy Policy).
One way to make money with ATM is by matching with a non-profit, company, or brand during “Brand Matching” and opting-in to receive messages through our in-app “Brand Messenger”, designed to protect your privacy from unwanted third party emails, texts, and phone calls. The money earned from this activity is paid to you directly from ATM.com. The companies themselves are not paying you, but instead ATM.com derives advertising revenue from companies and brands featured in our Brand Matching section. A portion of ATM.com’s advertising revenue is used to pay you for matches you accept. ATM.com can pay you rewards for actions leading to ATM.com earning commissions from Brands. Actions can include placing calls with a minimum duration, receiving a quote, going to 3rd party websites to shop, buy, order services, fill out lead forms, or respond to surveys. If you leave the ATM.com app through a link in our Brand Messenger, it is up to you to decide what information you wish to share with third party brands when calling, shopping, buying, and filling out lead forms. Just know that ATM.com does not share your personal information with brands. 
With ATM.com you can earn passively through Colony Dividends, whereby the aggregate data of everyone can create value for you, and market or medical research. These anonymized products do not disclose any personally identifiable information. We will de-identify and aggregate information collected through the app for all users so that this information can no longer be linked by 3rd parties (such as brands) to you or your device. 
Your Dividends once earned will be credited to your ATM.com account. Brand Matching earnings are credited instantly; Reward Dividends may be in a pending state for up to 30 days based on reporting limitations with 3rd party companies and networks. Colony Dividends will be paid within 30 days of our receipt of the revenue. 
Once your ATM.com account balance is greater than $20.00, you may withdraw cash in excess of the $20.00 minimum account balance reserve. For example, if your account balance is $82.00, you may transfer up to $62.00 to your linked Bank Account. This minimum reserve allows us to pay you faster and offers ATM.com protection from fraud.

record.primary_description:
Identity Theft Protection is hard. We make it easy for you with the LIFELOCK IDENTITY app and a NORTON 360 or LIFELOCK plan. You’re across town—and someone is taking out a bank loan in your name. We’ll send you an identity alert†. If it’s not you taking out that loan, you can respond right away, and we’ll go to work on your behalf.
LIFELOCK PLANS INCLUDE:
• LIFELOCK IDENTITY ALERT™ SYSTEM†: Alerts you if your Social Security Number, name, address, or date of birth are used in applications for credit or services.
• DARK WEB MONITORING: Continuously patrols the dark web and notifies you if we find your information.
• US-BASED ID RESTORATION SPECIALISTS: Should you become a victim of identity theft, an Agent will be dedicated to your case from start to finish to help restore your identity. 
• MILLION DOLLAR PROTECTION PACKAGE†††: If you become a victim of identity theft, you’ll be covered for lawyers and experts up to $1 million, and stolen funds and expense reimbursement up to the limits of your plan. 
ADVANTAGE AND ULTIMATE PLUS PLANS ALSO INCLUDE:
• EASY ACCESS TO CREDIT SCORE(S) & REPORT(S)1: Access to unlimited daily or monthly credit information (based on your selected plan), an essential part of credit protection. 
• IDENTITY LOCK: With a single tap, lock your TransUnion credit file.‡
• TRANSACTION MONITORING: Monitors your bank, credit card, and retirement account activity.†
NORTON 360 plans without LifeLock include dark web monitoring only.
LIFELOCK IDENTITY ADVISOR includes dark web monitoring, breach notifications, and merchant resolution management. It does not include the Million Dollar Protection™ Package or additional alert features offered in higher-tiered plans.
No one can prevent all identity theft or cybercrime.
1 If your plan includes credit reports, scores, and/or credit monitoring features ("Credit Features"), two requirements must be met to receive said features: (i) your identity must be successfully verified with Equifax; and (ii) Equifax must be able to locate your credit file and it must contain sufficient credit history information. IF EITHER OF THE FOREGOING REQUIREMENTS ARE NOT MET YOU WILL NOT RECEIVE CREDIT FEATURES FROM ANY BUREAU. If your plan also includes Credit Features from Experian and/or TransUnion, the above verification process must also be successfully completed with Experian and/or TransUnion, as applicable. If verification is successfully completed with Equifax, but not with Experian and/or TransUnion, as applicable, you will not receive Credit Features from such bureau(s) until the verification process is successfully completed and until then you will only receive Credit Features from Equifax. Any credit monitoring from Experian and TransUnion will take several days to begin after your successful LifeLock plan enrollment.
The credit scores provided are VantageScore 3.0 credit scores based on data from Equifax, Experian and TransUnion, respectively. Any One-Bureau VantageScore mentioned is based on Equifax data only. Third parties use many different types of credit scores and are likely to use a different type of credit score to assess your creditworthiness.
† We do not monitor all transactions at all businesses.
††† Reimbursement and Expense Compensation, each with limits of up to $1 million for Ultimate Plus, up to $100,000 for Advantage and up to $25,000 for Standard and Select (Norton 360 with LifeLock Select). And up to $1 million for coverage for lawyers and experts if needed, for all plans. Benefits under the Master Policy are issued and covered by United Specialty Insurance Company (State National Insurance Company, Inc. for NY State members). Policy terms, conditions and exclusions at: LifeLock.com/legal.
‡ Locking or Unlocking your credit file does not affect your credit score and does not stop all companies and agencies from pulling your credit file. The credit lock on your TransUnion file will be unlocked if your subscription is downgraded or cancelled.
record.name: LifeLock Identity by Norton

record.primary_description:
Pickup – Scan – Amend
With Amend you can get rewarded for helping out a local business and throwing away your garbage. Whether you purchased a cup of coffee or picked up someone else’s littered cup of coffee, Amend wants to reward you for properly disposing of garbage.
Why Amend?
Chances are you already throw away your garbage and in that case you can get rewarded for it! Think of it as a loyalty program with a tangible purpose. The problem is that not everybody throws away their garbage. Canadians produce approximately 31 million tonnes of garbage a year and on average 6 million tonnes become litter every year. That is the problem Amend is trying to solve. If we can make people conscious of what they do with their garbage we can decrease that number even slightly. If that fails, we can reward the people who pick up the litter and we think those people really do deserve rewarding.
How Do We Amend?
Amend partners with local businesses that care about making a difference. There is also a tangible incentive, that is that litter is bad advertising. People who see litter from that same company more than once begin to create a negative connotation with that company. That tangible incentive is what we believe will make reducing litter more than just a good cause, but something all businesses will pursue. That is the value for companies and that is how Amend rewards you for throwing out your/other people's garbage.

record.name: Zurich
record.description:
Rechtliche Hinweise: http://www.zurich.de/social-media

Wer wir sind

Ganz einfach: ein Versicherer – die Zurich Gruppe Deutschland. Wir bieten
•	Altersvorsorge, Sachversicherungen und Risikoschutz für Privatkunden
•	Individuelle Lösungen für Firmenkunden

Wir gehören zu einer weltweiten Versicherungsgruppe, der Zurich Insurance Group. In Deutschland gehören wir zu den Top Ten der Versicherungsbranche, mit rund 5.600 Mitarbeitern.

Erfahrt mehr über uns auf unserer Website:
http://www.zurich.de/versicherung/ueberuns/ueberuns.htm 


Warum "Zurich"?

Wir heißen "Zurich", weil das Stammhaus des Unternehmens – damals noch "Zürich Versicherungs-Verein" – in dieser Stadt entstand. Das war 1872. Aus dem "ü" wurde ein "u", weil es uns inzwischen auf der ganzen Welt gibt. Das "u" ist die internationale Schreibweise – ausgesprochen wird es nach vor wie in "Zürich".


So erreicht ihr uns

Das Facebook-Team von Zurich hilft euch gerne weiter – bei welchem Anliegen auch immer. Schreibt uns einfach eine Nachricht auf Facebook! Wir sind von Montag bis Freitag, jeweils 9 bis 18 Uhr für euch da.

In Versicherungsfragen erreicht ihr uns über die Service-Nummer
	+49 (0)228 268-01 (Gebühren abhängig vom Anbieter)

Ihr seid bei uns versichert und euch ist etwas passiert? Ruft an bei unserer Hotline für Schadenfälle (Inland):
        +49 (0)228 268-2680 (Gebühren abhängig vom Anbieter)
        Montag bis Freitag, 7 bis 20 Uhr

Für Rückrufwünsche erreicht ihr uns auch per SMS unter 01776-ZURICH (+49 (0)1776-987424). Die Kosten pro SMS richten sich nach eurem aktuellen Mobilfunkvertrag. Es fallen keine zusätzlichen Gebühren an. Sofern ihr eine SMS-Flatrate vereinbart habt, ist die Nutzung für euch kostenlos.
Oder ihr geht auf unsere Website: http://www.zurich.de/versicherung/service/service.htm


Eine Bitte ...

Haltet euch an die Regeln der Höflichkeit und geht so mit uns und den anderen Fans um, wie ihr selbst behandelt werden wollt.

Unhöfliche, beleidigende oder politisch unkorrekte Kommentare löschen wir. Falls jemand mehrfach solche Inhalte oder Kommentare postet, sperren wir ihn.


Unsere Produkte

Schaut doch mal auf unserer Website vorbei und informiert euch über unsere Leistungen:

http://www.zurich.de/versicherung/privatkunden/privatkunden.htm
•	Firmenkunden:
http://www.zurich.de/versicherung/firmenkunden/firmenkunden.htm

record.name: RCT - Rugby Club Toulonnais
record.description:
Le RCT est né en 1908 à la suite de la fusion du l'Étoile sportive varoise fondé en 1902 et de la fraction toulonnaise du Stade varois.
Le Rugby Club Toulonnais s'installe au Stade Mayol au début de la saison 1920-21. 
En 1931, c'est la reconnaissance avec le premier titre en championnat de France contre le Lyon olympique universitaire. Après quatre finales perdues (1948, 1968, 1971, 1985), le club varois remporte avec une génération exceptionnelle (Manu Diaz, Bernard Herrero, Éric Champ, Gilbert Doucet, Jérôme Gallion, Jérôme Bianchi...) un second titre en 1987 face au Racing Club de France, puis récidive en 1992 avec une équipe de minots comptant notamment dans ses rangs Yann Delaigue ou Marc de Rougemont. Confronté à des problèmes financiers le club est relégué en ProD2 en 2000. C'est sous l'impulsion d'un nouveau président, Mourad Boudjellal, et l'arrivée de stars internationales (Tana Umaga , Victor Matfield, Jerry Collins, Sonny Bill Williams, Jonny Wilkinson, George Smith, Paul Sackey,...)que le club retrouvera enfin l'élite. Ces dernières années, le club fut champion de France de ProD2 2005  et 2008, finaliste du Challenge Européen en 2010 et Champion d'Europe 2013 contre Clermont.
Plus de détails : http://www.rctoulon.com/fr/page/histoire/

Le palmarès du RCT 
*Champion de France : 1931, 1987 et 1992
*Heineken-Cup : Champion d'Europe 2013
*Finaliste du TOP 14 : 2012
*Pro D2 : 2005 et 2008
*Coup de France (Challenge Yves-du-Manoir) : 1934 et 1970 
*Challenge Européen : Finaliste 2010 et 2012

record.name: T24
record.description:
Hiçbir kişi, kurum, kuruluş ve oluşumla doğrudan, dolaylı ya da rastlantısal bir ilişkisi bulunmayan bağımsız internet gazetesi T24, 1 Eylül 2009’da yayına başladı.

T24; çalışmaları Türkiye’deki başlıca gazetecilik ödüllerine değer görülen Doğan Akın’ın yönetiminde kurucu editörler Metin Yener, Belde Bozkurt Oral ve Selin Ongun tarafından yayına hazırlandı, kurucu yazarlar Aydın Engin ve Oya Baydar ile yola koyuldu. Kurucu ekibe editör olarak katılan Hazal Özvarış, yazı işleri müdürlüğünü üstlendi.

Finansal dayatma ve ideolojik takıntılardan bağımsız gazetecilikte Türkiye’de önemli bir dönemeci ifade eden T24, yayına başladıktan kısa bir süre sonra, 2010 yılında, Türkiye Gazeteciler Cemiyeti’nin çalışmalarını ödüle değer gördüğü tek internet gazetesi oldu. T24 yazarlarından Hasan Cemal, Harvard Üniversitesi Nieman Gazetecilik Vakfı'nın "Dürüstlük ve Vicdan Ödülü"nü Türkiye'den alan (2015) ilk ve tek gazeteci oldu.

T24; hiçbir görüş ve inancı haberciliğin önüne koymayan, insanları, inançları, görüşleri dışlamayan yayın politikası, haberciliği, dosyaları ve söyleşileri ile Türkiye’de bütün kesimlerin güvendiği bir mecra olarak öne çıktı.

Kısa bir zamanda medyada en çok referans gösterilen az sayıda mecra arasına giren T24, bağımsız gazeteciliğin kurumlaşması yolunda Türkiye’de gerçekleştirilen en ciddi projelerden biri olarak yayınlarını sürdürüyor.
